aa(lp299
VTS: From what I've now learnt,
p300
aVmy actions that night in 1996 were a self-centered taking.
p301
aVI felt deserving of Thordis's body.
p302
aVI've had primarily positive social influences
p303
aVand examples of equitable behavior around me.
p304
aVBut on that occasion,
p305
aVI chose to draw upon the negative ones.
p306
aVThe ones that see women as having less intrinsic worth,
p307
aVand of men having some unspoken and symbolic claim to their bodies.
p308
aVThese influences I speak of are external to me, though.
p309
aVAnd it was only me in that room making choices,
p310
aVnobody else.
p311
aa(lp312
VWhen you own something
p313
aVand really square up to your culpability,
p314
aVI do think a surprising thing can happen.
p315
aVIt's what I call a paradox of ownership.
p316
aVI thought I'd buckle under the weight of responsibility.
p317
aVI thought my certificate of humanity would be burnt.
p318
aVInstead, I was offered to really own what I did,
p319
aVand found that it didn't possess the entirety of who I am.
p320
aVPut simply,
p321
aVsomething you've done doesn't have to constitute the sum of who you are.
p322
aVThe noise in my head abated.
p323
aVThe indulgent self-pity was starved of oxygen,
p324
aVand it was replaced with the clean air of acceptance \u2014
p325
aVan acceptance that I did hurt this wonderful person standing next to me;
p326
aVan acceptance that I am part of a large and shockingly everyday grouping of men
p327
aVwho have been sexually violent toward their partners.
p328
aa(lp329
VDon't underestimate the power of words.
p330
aVSaying to Thordis that I raped her changed my accord with myself,
p331
aVas well as with her.
p332
aVBut most importantly,
p333
aVthe blame transferred from Thordis to me.
p334
aVFar too often,
p335
aVthe responsibility is attributed to female survivors of sexual violence,
p336
aVand not to the males who enact it.
p337
aVFar too often,
p338
aVthe denial and running leaves all parties at a great distance from the truth.
p339
aVThere's definitely a public conversation happening now,
p340
aVand like a lot of people,
p341
aVwe're heartened that there's less retreating
p342
aVfrom this difficult but important discussion.
p343
aVI feel a real responsibility to add our voices to it.
